            <title>[KAFKA-9014] AssertionError thrown by SourceRecordWriteCounter when SourceTask.poll returns an empty list</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-9014</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When creating a custom SourceConnectorTask where the implementation of `poll()` returns an empty List, the connector crashes with an AssertionError.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
