                            <comment id="16949843" author="kkonstantine" created="Fri, 11 Oct 2019 23:50:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The method contract mentions specifically that `null` is expected when the connector has no records to return. But I also agree that, without deprecating this behavior, returning an empty list of records should not crash the task. Added the PR above with a possible fix based on this assumption. &lt;br/&gt;
